### Créer un utilisateur
POST {{base}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Jean",
  "lastName": "Dupont",
  "email": "etudiant@univ.fr",
  "password": "password123",
  "category": "STUDENT"
}

###

### Lister les utilisateurs
GET {{base}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}

###

### Bloquer un utilisateur
PATCH {{base}}/api/users/COLLER_UN_USER_ID_ICI/block
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}

###

### Créer un ouvrage
POST {{base}}/api/works
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "title": "Clean Code",
  "isbn": "9780132350884",
  "authors": "Robert C. Martin",
  "publisher": "Prentice Hall",
  "year": 2008,
  "language": "EN",
  "subjects": "Software Engineering"
}

###

### Ajouter un exemplaire
POST {{base}}/api/works/0753f42f-dfce-4f03-bb59-943f87daa5c6/copies
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "barcode": "BC0012024",
  "campusId": "CAMPUS-A",
  "shelf": "INF-42",
  "condition": "NEUF"
}

###

### Changer le statut d'un exemplaire
PATCH {{base}}/api/copies/COLLER_UN_COPY_ID_ICI/status
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "status": "IN_PROCESSING"
}

###

### Enregistrer un emprunt
POST {{base}}/api/loans
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Idempotency-Key: loan-001-2024

{
  "copyId": "COLLER_UN_COPY_ID_ICI",
  "userId": "COLLER_UN_USER_ID_ICI"
}

###

### Enregistrer un retour
POST {{base}}/api/loans/return?copyId=COLLER_UN_COPY_ID_ICI
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Idempotency-Key: return-001-2024

###

### Déclarer un exemplaire perdu
POST {{base}}/api/loans/COLLER_UN_LOAN_ID_ICI/lost
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}

###

### Valider le retrait d'une réservation
POST {{base}}/api/holds/COLLER_UN_HOLD_ID_ICI/pickup
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}

###

### Créer une pénalité
POST {{base}}/api/penalties
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "userId": "COLLER_UN_USER_ID_ICI",
  "reason": "Retard de 7 jours",
  "amount": 0.70
}

###

### Lever une pénalité
POST {{base}}/api/penalties/COLLER_UN_PENALTY_ID_ICI/clear
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}

###

### Consulter les pénalités d'un utilisateur
GET {{base}}/api/penalties?userId=COLLER_UN_USER_ID_ICI
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}

###

### Reporting (refusé — ADMIN requis)
GET {{base}}/api/reports/top-loans
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenLibrarian}}


