}

###

### Créer un compte ADMIN
POST {{base}}/api/users
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "firstName": "Admin",
  "lastName": "Système",
  "email": "admin@univ.fr",
  "password": "password123",
  "category": "ADMIN"
}

###

### Consulter la politique STUDENT
GET {{base}}/api/policies/STUDENT
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}

###

### Modifier la politique STUDENT
PUT {{base}}/api/policies/STUDENT
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "maxLoans": 5,
  "loanDurationDays": 21,
  "maxRenewals": 2,
  "overdueBlockThresholdDays": 14,
  "penaltyType": "PER_DAY",
  "penaltyAmount": 0.10,
  "pickupDelayDays": 3
}

###

### Modifier la politique TEACHER
PUT {{base}}/api/policies/TEACHER
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "maxLoans": 20,
  "loanDurationDays": 60,
  "maxRenewals": 3,
  "overdueBlockThresholdDays": 30,
  "penaltyType": "PER_DAY",
  "penaltyAmount": 0.20,
  "pickupDelayDays": 3
}

###

### Top 10 des ouvrages les plus empruntés
GET {{base}}/api/reports/top-loans?limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}

###

### Prêts en retard
GET {{base}}/api/reports/overdue
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}

###

### Rapport d'acquisitions (dernier mois)
GET {{base}}/api/reports/acquisitions?from=2026-03-01T00:00:00Z&to=2026-04-30T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{tokenAdmin}}
